we would normally do pyramid?

00:03:16.863 --> 00:03:19.332 line:5%,start
I think it's really strange
that Melissa's having

00:03:19.399 --> 00:03:21.234 line:5%,start
secret meetings with Abby now.

00:03:21.301 --> 00:03:23.002 line:95%,end
I mean, why wouldn't
she have at least told

00:03:23.069 --> 00:03:24.270 line:95%,end
the other moms she was going?

00:03:24.337 --> 00:03:26.706 line:95%,end
I don't know
if Abby really will even come back.

00:03:26.973 --> 00:03:28.408 line:95%,end
Hey, guys.

00:03:28.474 --> 00:03:30.543 line:95%,end
Girls, listen,
can you guys just go to studio A

00:03:30.643 --> 00:03:31.978 line:95%,end
- and start stretching?
- HOLLY: Super.


00:03:32.045 --> 00:03:33.046 line:5%,start
- OK.
- Go, go, go.

00:03:33.112 --> 00:03:35.515 line:5%,start
I finally spoke to Abby
and I'm in charge of the routines

00:03:35.582 --> 00:03:36.749 line:5%,start
again this week.

00:03:36.816 --> 00:03:38.484 line:95%,end
I hope I can pull off
another win without her.

00:03:38.551 --> 00:03:40.053 line:95%,end
So I did talk to Abby.

00:03:40.119 --> 00:03:41.754 line:95%,end
We're definitely competing this weekend.

00:03:41.821 --> 00:03:44.123 line:95%,end
- WOMAN: OK.
- So do we know who's doing dances?

00:03:44.190 --> 00:03:45.191 line:95%,end
Yes.

00:03:48.127 --> 00:03:49.295 line:95%,end
Chloe solo.

00:03:49.362 --> 00:03:50.830 line:95%,end
Oh, OK.

00:03:50.897 --> 00:03:52.332 line:95%,end
Abby already knows
that she's giving Maddie

00:03:52.398 --> 00:03:54.767 line:95%,end
a solo at nationals
but she isn't sure who else.

00:03:54.834 --> 00:03:57.337 line:95%,end
She wants me to work with Chloe
on the lyrical piece,

00:03:57.403 --> 00:03:58.571 line:95%,end
which is her best style.

00:03:58.638 --> 00:04:00.206 line:95%,end
So Christi better not have any complaints.

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:03.109 line:95%,end
Group dance, I'm guessing with everyone.

00:04:03.176 --> 00:04:04.911 line:95%,end
- I haven't heard yet.
- =OK.

00:04:04.978 --> 00:04:06.746 line:95%,end
It's a dark contemporary routine.

00:04:06.813 --> 00:04:11.851 line:95%,end
And, um, no Maddie solo,
but she said she wants

00:04:11.918 --> 00:04:14.487 line:95%,end
- to feature Maddie in the group.
- OK. OK.

00:04:14.554 --> 00:04:16.289 line:95%,end
And Asia and Kenzie duet.

00:04:16.389 --> 00:04:19.626 line:95%,end
HOLLY: Oh, that'll be good.

00:04:19.692 --> 00:04:22.061 line:95%,end
So that's only three numbers.

00:04:22.128 --> 00:04:24.297 line:5%,start
I'm happy for the other girls this week,

00:04:24.364 --> 00:04:27.000 line:5%,start
but I have to be honest, I'm really mad

00:04:27.066 --> 00:04:28.935 line:95%,end
that Kendall doesn't have a solo
this week.

00:04:29.002 --> 00:04:32.772 line:95%,end
With only a few weeks till nationals,
these solos are everything.

00:04:33.072 --> 00:04:35.708 line:95%,end
And Kendall needs to prove to Abby
that she can handle

00:04:35.775 --> 00:04:37.644 line:95%,end
competing on a national level.

00:04:37.710 --> 00:04:41.414 line:95%,end
And I don't know how she can do that
with no solo and no Abby.

00:04:41.514 --> 00:04:44.917 line:95%,end
Is she coming this weekend or ever?
Or this week?

00:04:44.984 --> 00:04:47.253 line:95%,end
- Is she coming today?
- She didn't say she wasn't.

00:04:47.387 --> 00:04:48.888 line:95%,end
You're just gonna start rehearsal,

00:04:48.955 --> 00:04:50.456 line:95%,end
no pyramid, no nothing.

00:04:50.523 --> 00:04:52.525 line:95%,end
- This was pyramid.
- WOMAN: Pyramid.

00:04:52.592 --> 00:04:54.327 line:95%,end
Yay.

00:04:59.165 --> 00:05:00.600 line:95%,end
CATHY: Hey, everybody.

00:05:00.667 --> 00:05:02.368 line:95%,end
KIDS: Hi.

00:05:02.435 --> 00:05:06.673 line:95%,end
It's nice to see my special teams
and my special moms.

00:05:06.973 --> 00:05:08.775 line:95%,end
And, Zack, you're back.

00:05:08.841 --> 00:05:10.743 line:95%,end
You know,
that's kinda like the battle cry.

00:05:10.810 --> 00:05:11.911 line:95%,end
Zack is back.

00:05:11.978 --> 00:05:14.514 line:5%,start
Zack has been off working professionally

00:05:14.580 --> 00:05:16.416 line:95%,end
and now he's back with our team.

00:05:16.516 --> 00:05:19.085 line:95%,end
With him back, hopefully we can beat Abby.

00:05:19.152 --> 00:05:21.087 line:95%,end
I'm not the least bit concerned

00:05:21.354 --> 00:05:23.656 line:95%,end
that Anthony isn't here right now.

00:05:23.723 --> 00:05:25.958 line:95%,end
I think he was an avalanche.

00:05:26.025 --> 00:05:28.428 line:95%,end
He was a accident waiting to happen.

00:05:28.561 --> 00:05:31.130 line:95%,end
Anthony has not produced
a win for me in a while

00:05:31.197 --> 00:05:32.865 line:95%,end
and I'm a little frustrated by that.

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:37.537 line:95%,end
So without Anthony being here,
I feel as though I can focus more

00:05:37.603 --> 00:05:39.906 line:95%,end
on nationals,
which is right down the road.

00:05:39.972 --> 00:05:42.208 line:95%,end
And I don't have
to play referee between him

00:05:42.275 --> 00:05:43.843 line:95%,end
and the parents and the stress level.

00:05:43.910 --> 00:05:45.578 line:95%,end
You want to see me in your face?

00:05:45.645 --> 00:05:46.913 line:95%,end
You will never be in my face.

00:05:47.647 --> 00:05:49.248 line:95%,end
Let me go for where I'm going, please.

00:05:49.349 --> 00:05:50.683 line:95%,end
CATHY: Your choreography is in jeopardy.

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:52.685 line:95%,end
- He's a puppet. This is a puppet.
- CATHY: He looks dumb.

00:05:52.752 --> 00:05:54.053 line:95%,end
- CATHY: No.
- Yes.

00:05:54.721 --> 00:06:00.793 line:95%,end
So last time that we competed,
we did a seasons contemporary number

00:06:05.898 --> 00:06:07.767 line:95%,end
and we got rained on.

00:06:08.334 --> 00:06:09.602 line:95%,end
We didn't win.

00:06:09.669 --> 00:06:14.073 line:95%,end
The last competition,
we lost to Abby again.

00:06:14.140 --> 00:06:18.010 line:95%,end
And with nationals
not being but a few weeks away,

00:06:18.111 --> 00:06:21.614 line:95%,end
it's essential that we have a good showing
at this competition.

00:06:21.681 --> 00:06:27.487 line:95%,end
Let's begin,
starting with my bottom Apple, Zack.

00:06:27.553 --> 00:06:28.888 line:95%,end
No surprises there.

00:06:28.955 --> 00:06:31.591 line:95%,end
It's hard to be at the top
when you aren't with us performing.

00:06:31.657 --> 00:06:33.459 line:95%,end
You're wonderful.
You can move up.

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:37.530 line:95%,end
Next, we have Mary.

00:06:39.165 --> 00:06:41.768 line:95%,end
Mary struggled a little bit
the last time that we saw you.

00:06:41.834 --> 00:06:43.936 line:95%,end
We talked about her port de bras arms.

00:06:44.437 --> 00:06:46.339 line:5%,start
Mary is a beautiful dancer

00:06:46.406 --> 00:06:49.442 line:5%,start
and I think Kathy is crazy for putting her
on the bottom of the Apple tree.

00:06:49.509 --> 00:06:51.077 line:95%,end
It's an insult to the dance community.

00:06:51.144 --> 00:06:53.513 line:95%,end
Everybody that sees Mary
knows she's trained.

00:06:53.579 --> 00:06:54.614 line:95%,end
She shouldn't be there.

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:55.882 line:95%,end
CATHY: Let's move on.

00:06:57.283 --> 00:06:59.285 line:95%,end
Kaya, you're like in the middle.

00:06:59.352 --> 00:07:03.156 line:95%,end
You can no longer be the one
that's not professionally trained,


00:07:03.689 --> 00:07:06.159 line:95%,end
be the one
that doesn't have technical classes.

00:07:06.225 --> 00:07:10.163 line:5%,start
Excuse me that I couldn't afford
to put my daughter in $1,000 classes,

00:07:10.229 --> 00:07:12.532 line:95%,end
but I've never used that as an excuse.

00:07:12.598 --> 00:07:14.801 line:95%,end
I'll don't need excuses.
Nicaya's the best.

00:07:14.867 --> 00:07:15.935 line:95%,end
CATHY: Let's move on.

00:07:16.002 --> 00:07:20.106 line:95%,end
OK. So Had, I'm being
a little bit more aggressive this week.

00:07:20.173 --> 00:07:22.708 line:95%,end
It's been a while since I've gotten a win.

00:07:22.775 --> 00:07:26.446 line:95%,end
There's no room for error--
none.

00:07:26.512 --> 00:07:29.282 line:5%,start
I think Hadley should be at the top
of the apple tree.

00:07:29.348 --> 00:07:32.084 line:95%,end
I mean, she works the hardest,
I work the hardest,

00:07:32.151 --> 00:07:34.387 line:95%,end
and together, we should be rewarded.

00:07:34.454 --> 00:07:35.988 line:95%,end
CATHY: It's easy to figure out

00:07:36.055 --> 00:07:38.691 line:95%,end
that our leading man this week is Lucas.

00:07:38.758 --> 00:07:42.528 line:95%,end
Lucas, being at the top
makes you that guy

00:07:42.595 --> 00:07:44.363 line:95%,end
who has to go into battle this week

00:07:44.430 --> 00:07:46.032 line:95%,end
and lead your team.

00:07:46.098 --> 00:07:47.900 line:95%,end
Nationals are approaching fast

00:07:47.967 --> 00:07:50.603 line:95%,end
and I need to see who can lead me
to a victory this week

00:07:50.670 --> 00:07:51.671 line:95%,end
and at nationals.

00:07:51.737 --> 00:07:54.407 line:95%,end
I'm hoping that Lucas is the guy
that can do that.

00:07:54.507 --> 00:07:57.143 line:95%,end
This week, we are going
to Charleston, West Virginia

00:07:57.210 --> 00:07:59.412 line:95%,end
for the Masters of Dance Competition.

00:07:59.479 --> 00:08:03.216 line:95%,end
I know that the Abby Lee Dance Company
will be at the competition this week.

00:08:03.316 --> 00:08:06.686 line:95%,end
Our group dance
is going to be Rise of the Phoenix.

00:08:06.752 --> 00:08:09.755 line:95%,end
