to just rise up on stage

00:08:09.856 --> 00:08:11.290 line:95%,end
and just capitalize.

00:08:11.991 --> 00:08:16.729 line:95%,end
I know first handedly,
because I sold on social media

00:08:16.829 --> 00:08:20.766 line:95%,end
and maybe some of you did as well,
Chloe is doing a solo

00:08:20.833 --> 00:08:22.101 line:95%,end
at the competition this week.

00:08:22.168 --> 00:08:25.671 line:95%,end
I think that Chloe is not as strong
as she used to be.

00:08:25.938 --> 00:08:29.876 line:95%,end
I need a dancer that can
beat Chloe this weekend.

00:08:29.942 --> 00:08:34.747 line:95%,end
My solo is going to be given to Zack.

00:08:34.814 --> 00:08:36.449 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:08:36.516 --> 00:08:38.618 line:95%,end
ZACK: I'm so happy
to have a solo this week.

00:08:38.684 --> 00:08:40.086 line:95%,end
I've beat Chloe in the past.

